Warned of the imminence of a wonderful event, he looked through the railed head of his bed at the white door and waited for it to open and the prediction to come true. But the door did not open. Suddenly, to one side, beyond his field of vision, something stirred. Under the cover of a large screen someone was standing and laughing. 'I'm coming, I'm coming, just a moment,' muttered Luzhin, freeing his legs from the sheet and lookin